# TGLC XRPL Platform

## Structure
- `api/` - FastAPI backend (Python)
- `web/` - Next.js frontend (TypeScript)
- `scripts/` - Admin scripts

## Dependencies
- Backend: fastapi, uvicorn, xrpl-py, python-dotenv, pydantic
- Frontend: next, react, xrpl, xrpl-connect, zustand, lucide-react, clsx, tailwind-merge

## XRPL SDK Patterns
- Use `Client` with WebSocket URLs (wss://)
- Use `client.fundWallet()` for testnet wallet creation
- Use `client.submitAndWait(tx, { autofill: true, wallet })` for transactions
- Use `xrpToDrops()` for XRP amount conversion

## Code Style
- Minimal, no verbose comments
- Python: type hints, PEP 8
- TypeScript: strict mode, functional components
- No markdown in code files

## Environment
- Testnet: wss://s.altnet.rippletest.net:51233
- Mainnet: wss://xrplcluster.com/
- Configure via XRPL_NETWORK env var
